<chapter xml:id="summarizing-data">
  <title>Summarizing data</title>
  
  <introduction>
    <p>
      This chapter covers methods for summarizing and describing data using statistical measures.
    </p>
  </introduction>

  <section xml:id="measures-of-central-tendency">
    <title>Measures of central tendency</title>
    <p>
      Central tendency measures include the mean, median, and mode.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section xml:id="measures-of-variability">
    <title>Measures of variability</title>
    <p>
      Variability measures describe how spread out the data are.
    </p>
  </section>
</chapter>
